WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.500
Ukraine has hit Russia with the biggest strike since the start of the war.

2
00:00:04.500 --> 00:00:08.500
Moscow's skyline blackened with smoke after hundreds of drones struck

3
00:00:08.500 --> 00:00:11.500
and set fire to a major oil refinery overnight.

4
00:00:11.500 --> 00:00:17.000
Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelensky is seeking support from the United States and Europe

5
00:00:17.000 --> 00:00:19.500
to reach a deal to end the war.

